## Zero Tolerance Baseline Verification

| Criterion | Status |
|---|---|
| No implicit permissions | ✅ Policy deny-by-default |
| No hidden state | ✅ All state in kernel-managed channels |
| Deterministic execution | ✅ Single-threaded, sorted dispatch, monotonic ordering |
| No audit bypass | ✅ Every mutation audited |
| No privilege escalation | ✅ Parent-authorized delegation with role checks |
| No silent drops | ✅ DLQ + audit on every routing failure |
| No code suppressions | ✅ 0 `# pylint`, `# type`, `# noqa`, `# nosec` |

